<div class="row mb-4">
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card p-3" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);">
      <h6 class="text-muted">Total Santri</h6>
      <h3 style="color:var(--primary);"><%= totalSantri %></h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card p-3" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-light);">
      <h6 class="text-muted">Total Guru</h6>
      <h3 style="color:var(--primary-light);"><%= totalGuru %></h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card p-3" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);">
      <h6 class="text-muted">Total Halaqoh</h6>
      <h3 style="color:var(--secondary);"><%= totalHalaqoh %></h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card p-3" style="border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;">
      <h6 class="text-muted">Delete Requests</h6>
      <h3 style="color:#F59E0B;"><%= totalDeleteRequests %></h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12">
    <div class="card p-4">
      <h5><i class="bi bi-book me-2"></i>Selamat Datang di Halaqoh Tahfizh Dashboard</h5>
      <p class="text-muted mt-3">Dashboard ini digunakan untuk mengelola data santri, guru, halaqoh, serta melakukan analisis clustering performa hafalan menggunakan algoritma K-Means dengan Manhattan Distance.</p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <h6>Fitur Utama:</h6>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Dataset</strong> - Kelola dan lihat data santri</li>
          <li><strong>Clustering</strong> - Jalankan algoritma K-Means</li>
          <li><strong>Hasil</strong> - Lihat visualisasi cluster dan statistik Silhouette Score</li>
          <li><strong>Laporan</strong> - Export hasil analisis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
